00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.603
First private airline in russian history

00:00:03.603 --> 00:00:06.072
Transaero is a Russian airline. 

00:00:06.072 --> 00:00:10.010
It was the country's first private airline company.

00:00:10.010 --> 00:00:14.914
Founded on November 5th 1991,
it has recently turned 20. 

00:00:14.914 --> 00:00:19.386
We have around 156 destinations worldwide

00:00:19.386 --> 00:00:25.025
from the international airport 
of Moscow Domodedovo.

00:00:25.025 --> 00:00:31.097
The fleet is made up of 70 aircraft -

00:00:31.097 --> 00:00:32.465
Boeings and Tupolevs.

00:00:32.465 --> 00:00:36.803
We will soon have the Airbus A320 Neo.

00:00:36.803 --> 00:00:40.673
Lyon-Moscow, 2 flights a week

00:00:40.673 --> 00:00:44.944
Leaving from Lyon, 
we have two direct flights a week.

00:00:44.944 --> 00:00:51.551
Flights generally last 3 hrs 40 mins

00:00:51.551 --> 00:00:54.254
onboard a Boeing 737.

00:00:54.254 --> 00:01:00.160
Flights leave from T2 on Wednesdays 
and Saturdays at 1.45pm.

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:04.197
Moscow, an international metropolis 
of a thousand faces

00:01:04.197 --> 00:01:10.336
Moscow is the capital of Russia 
but also of business.

00:01:10.336 --> 00:01:17.143
The Moskva-City business centre 
is growing despite the crisis.

00:01:17.143 --> 00:01:21.614
Moscow makes it easy for foreign entrepreneurs,

00:01:21.614 --> 00:01:28.221
by organising meetings with Russian businesses.

00:01:28.221 --> 00:01:33.326
It is also possible to visit Moscow.

00:01:33.326 --> 00:01:41.868
The city is more than 800 years old 
and is home to remarkable sites:

00:01:41.868 --> 00:01:49.676
the Kremlin, the Red Square, surrounded by ornate Orthodox churches. 

00:01:49.676 --> 00:01:54.481
There is also the Puchkin Museum of Fine Arts, the Tretiakov Gallery,

00:01:54.481 --> 00:01:59.385
parks and monasteries. 

